This project is a fan recreation of the 1996 game "Z" by The Bitmap Brothers.
It is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by The Bitmap Brothers.

The original game "Z" was created by:
- The Bitmap Brothers
- Allan Acree
- Brad Stewart

This recreation uses:
- Godot Engine 4.x (godotengine.org)
- Various open-source libraries

The Zod Engine remake (zod.sourceforge.net) was an inspiration for this
project. The Zod Engine is licensed under GPLv3.

All original assets, code, and IP remain the property of The Bitmap Brothers.
